sub_title: International Market Executive at Bord Bia - The Irish Food Board
summary:
I am a recent graduate of Commerce International with German at UCD. 

I have recently started my new role as an International Market Executive at Bord Bia Amsterdam, where I will be promoting Irish food and drink in the Dutch market. 

Alongside this role, I have received a scholarship to complete a two-year MSc in Global Business Practice at the UCD Michael Smurfit Graduate Business School.
 
I'm a positive, passionate and creative person with a keen interest in International and EU affairs, as well as Marketing and Agribusiness. I hope to further my skills in these areas as I progress my education and career.
